{"id":"6426","name":"bright-early-blah-blah-blah-snow-edition","title":"Bright &amp; Early: Blah Blah Blah Snow Edition","author":"Christy Frink","date":"2011-01-25T10:30:00-06:00","tags":["american lung association","home burglaries","mnps","murfreesboro water and sewer department","nclb","smoking","snow","south nashville","winter weather"],"categories":["News"],"contentEncoded":"<div id=\"greet_block\"><noscript><div class=\"greet_block wpgb_cornered\"><div class=\"greet_text\"><div class=\"greet_image\"><a href=\"http://nashvillest.com/feed/rss/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"http://nashvillest.com/wp-content/plugins/wp-greet-box/images/rss_icon.png\" alt=\"WP Greet Box icon\"></a></div>Hello there! If you are new here, you might want to <a href=\"http://nashvillest.com/feed/rss/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>subscribe to the RSS feed</strong></a> for updates on this topic.<div style=\"clear:both\"></div><div class=\"greet_block_powered_by\">Powered by <a href=\"http://omninoggin.com/projects/wordpress-plugins/wp-greet-box-wordpress-plugin/\" title=\"WP Greet Box WordPress Plugin\" style=\"text-decoration:none;\">WP Greet Box</a> <a href=\"http://omninoggin.com/\" title=\"WordPress Plugin\" style=\"text-decoration:none;\">WordPress Plugin</a></div><div style=\"clear:both\"></div></div></div></noscript></div><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://www.flickr.com/photos/53089791@N02/5377763801/in/pool-715021@N24/\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;www.flickr.com&apos;]);\"><img class=\"aligncenter\" src=\"http://farm6.static.flickr.com/5048/5377763801_f4175e7014.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"333\"></a></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\">Good morning, Nashville. We&#x2019;re very sorry to do this to you two days in a row, but here is your abbreviated sprint through the morning news:</p><ul><li>Snow! The latest models show us in either 1-3&#x2033; or 2-4&#x2033;, depending on who you ask. Let&#x2019;s just say we wouldn&#x2019;t write off the possibility of another snow day for the children, who basically no longer go to school. [<a href=\"http://www.wkrn.com/Global/story.asp?S=13897269\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;www.wkrn.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\">WKRN</a>]</li><li>According to the American Lung Association, Tennessee sucks at helping smokers quit. [<a href=\"http://www.wkrn.com/Global/story.asp?S=13899416\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;www.wkrn.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\">WKRN</a>]</li><li>South Nashville home burglaries are up 22% and police are trying to figure out what to do about it. [<a href=\"http://www.wsmv.com/news/26606223/detail.html\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;www.wsmv.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\">WSMV</a>]</li><li>Metro Schools are hoping to appeal a mandate by the federal government that would allow students in failing schools to transfer to better ones. Though this is standard procedure for schools that aren&#x2019;t meeting No Child Left Behind standards, this year&#x2019;s unusual testing schedule would mean that students would be transferring in the middle of the school year. [<a href=\"http://wpln.org/?p=23420\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;wpln.org&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\">WPLN</a>]</li><li>Murfreesboro&#x2019;s Water and Sewer Department is now cutting off water to folks who are more than $100 overdue and at least two months behind. [<a href=\"http://www.newschannel5.com/story/13900570/hundreds-faced-with-no-running-water\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;www.newschannel5.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\">WTVF</a>]</li></ul><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><em>Photo by <a href=\"http://www.flickr.com/photos/53089791@N02/5377763801/in/pool-715021@N24/\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;www.flickr.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\">liebeststark</a>.</em></p><p>Related posts:<ol><li><a href=\"http://nashvillest.com/2011/01/28/bright-early-the-sun-also-rises-edition/\" rel=\"bookmark\" title=\"Permanent Link: Bright &amp; Early: The Sun Also Rises Edition\">Bright &amp; Early: The Sun Also Rises Edition</a></li><li><a href=\"http://nashvillest.com/2010/12/16/bright-early-a-drop-in-the-bucket-edition-2/\" rel=\"bookmark\" title=\"Permanent Link: Bright &amp; Early: A Drop In The Bucket Edition\">Bright &amp; Early: A Drop In The Bucket Edition</a></li><li><a href=\"http://nashvillest.com/2009/12/21/bright-early-its-never-going-to-snow-here-edition/\" rel=\"bookmark\" title=\"Permanent Link: Bright &amp; Early: It&#x2019;s Never Going To Snow Here Edition\">Bright &amp; Early: It&#x2019;s Never Going To Snow Here Edition</a></li><li><a href=\"http://nashvillest.com/2011/01/26/bright-early-oh-snow-it-didnt-edition/\" rel=\"bookmark\" title=\"Permanent Link: Bright &amp; Early: Oh Snow It Didn&#x2019;t Edition\">Bright &amp; Early: Oh Snow It Didn&#x2019;t Edition</a></li><li><a href=\"http://nashvillest.com/2011/01/20/bright-early-snow-etc-edition/\" rel=\"bookmark\" title=\"Permanent Link: Bright &amp; Early: Snow, Etc. Edition\">Bright &amp; Early: Snow, Etc. Edition</a></li></ol></p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<!--END .entry-content .article-->"}